title: Annual report
context: §200D-5 Annual report. The council shall submit an annual report on its activities to the governor and the legislature, which may include recommendations; provided that the recommendations are consistent with the purposes of this chapter. [L 1993, c 317, pt of §2, §7; am L 1998, c 4, §3; am L 2009, c 68, §1; am L 2010, c 19, §§3, 4]
